  {
    "content_id": 233503,
    "reference_id": 109027,
    "title": "希伯來書 6:13–20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "58006013-58006020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>神在<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108243\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">亞伯拉罕之</span><span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108253\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">約</span>中向<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108253\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">亞伯拉罕</span>應許。閱讀希伯來書的信徒知道這一點。他們也知道神已經實現了對亞伯拉罕的應許，神賜給了亞伯拉罕日後將成為以色列國的大家庭。希伯來書的作者用這個故事提醒讀者神的應許。神從不說謊，祂總是信守祂的應許。神對<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108215\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">世界</span>的目的不會改變，祂的目的是讓祂的<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108197\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">創造</span>永遠在<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108211\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">平安</span>中與祂同住。這是信徒所擁有的盼望。這個盼望是確定且牢靠的，因為它基於的是耶穌的<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108208\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">工作</span>。</p>",
